eqlMonitorEntry.name: eqlMonitorEntry
eqlMonitorEntry.description: An entry (row) containing information about hosts monitoring the group.

eqlMonitorIndex.name: eqlMonitorIndex
eqlMonitorIndex.description: This field specifies a unique index which identifies an monitoring instance. This field is a hash of the GUID.

eqlMonitorUUID.name: eqlMonitorUUID
eqlMonitorUUID.description: This field is for internal use only.

eqlMonitorServerName.name: eqlMonitorServerName
eqlMonitorServerName.description: This field specifies the DNS server name of the host running SANHQ monitoring the group. Together with eqlSANHQDomainName it must be a name which is resolvable by DNS. There is no default for SANHQDNSName.

eqlMonitorDomainName.name: eqlMonitorDomainName
eqlMonitorDomainName.description: This field specifies the DNS domain name of the host running SANHQ monitoring the group.

eqlMonitorInetAddressType.name: eqlMonitorInetAddressType
eqlMonitorInetAddressType.description: The ip address type of the host monitoring this group.

eqlMonitorInetAddress.name: eqlMonitorInetAddress
eqlMonitorInetAddress.description: The ip address, in network byte order, of the host monitoring this group.

eqlMonitorSupportAssist.name: eqlMonitorSupportAssist
eqlMonitorSupportAssist.description: This field specifies how SupportAssist is currently monitoring this group.

eqlMonitorTimestamp.name: eqlMonitorTimestamp
eqlMonitorTimestamp.description: This field specifies the last access time for SANHQ Monitoring. Time is represented as the time in seconds since 00:00:00 UTC, 1970-01-01.

eqlMonitorSupportAssistTimestamp.name: eqlMonitorSupportAssistTimestamp
eqlMonitorSupportAssistTimestamp.description: This field specifies the last access time for SupportAssist. Time is represented as the time in seconds since 00:00:00 UTC, 1970-01-01.

eqlMonitorLicensingTimestamp.name: eqlMonitorLicensingTimestamp
eqlMonitorLicensingTimestamp.description: This field specifies the last time SupportAssist sent licensing records to Dell. Time is represented as the time in seconds since 00:00:00 UTC, 1970-01-01.

eqlMonitorDescription.name: eqlMonitorDescription
eqlMonitorDescription.description: This field specifies a descriptive string that provides details about group monitoring. The description can be 128 octets. There is no default value.

eqlMonitorStatusEntry.name: eqlMonitorStatusEntry
eqlMonitorStatusEntry.description: An entry (row) containing status information about hosts monitoring the group.

eqlMonitorStatusReminder.name: eqlMonitorStatusReminder
eqlMonitorStatusReminder.description: This field indicates if the SANHQ currently monitoring this group has recently contacted the group.
